        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card">
          <h4>Related Conditions</h4>
          <ul class="sidebar-links">
            {relatedConditions.map(c => (
              <li><a href={c.href}>{c.label} →</a></li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="sidebar-card sidebar-card--review">
          <div class="sidebar-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"I had chronic lower back pain for two years and nothing helped. After six visits with Dr. Yager I was back to normal. Wish I had come sooner."</p>
          <strong>— ProHealth Patient</strong>
